      "snippet": "I would argue that just as much of a staple the Vatican and the Coliseum are in Rome, Trevi Fountain is right there with them. Just insanely beautiful and mesmerizing to look at, especially at night. During the day the fountain is bustling with visitors and may be hard to take a picture or good look at, so I would suggest going later in the evening or early in the morning to get a real good look at every piece of art that makes up the fountain.",
      "extracted_snippet": {
        "original": "I would argue that just as much of a staple the Vatican and the Coliseum are in Rome, Trevi Fountain is right there with them. Just insanely beautiful and mesmerizing to look at, especially at night. During the day the fountain is bustling with visitors and may be hard to take a picture or good look at, so I would suggest going later in the evening or early in the morning to get a real good look at every piece of art that makes up the fountain."
      },
