      "snippet": "The Trevi Fountain was absolutely magical. The fountain is stunning with the intricate sculptures and flowing water are even more impressive in person than in photos. Its picture perfect sans the crowd.\n\nThe area around the fountain is lively, with plenty of caf\u00e9s and gelaterias nearby, which makes for a great spot to soak in the atmosphere, but it can get very crowded.\n\nOverall, a must-see in Rome. Its iconic, beautiful, and full of charm!",
      "extracted_snippet": {
        "original": "The Trevi Fountain was absolutely magical. The fountain is stunning with the intricate sculptures and flowing water are even more impressive in person than in photos. Its picture perfect sans the crowd.\n\nThe area around the fountain is lively, with plenty of caf\u00e9s and gelaterias nearby, which makes for a great spot to soak in the atmosphere, but it can get very crowded.\n\nOverall, a must-see in Rome. Its iconic, beautiful, and full of charm!"
      },
